---
import PixelIcon from './PixelIcon.astro';
---

<section class="about reveal" id="about">
  <div class="about-container">
    <h2 class="section-heading">/about</h2>

    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-bio">
        <p class="about-text">
          <strong>High Performer. Deep Focus Founder.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="about-text">
          I build systems for those who value <strong>uninterrupted focus</strong> and <strong>deep sleep</strong>. 
          My work is centered around the <strong>Focus Sprint (Frint)</strong> philosophy: 
          measuring focus depth, length, and frequency to optimize performance across all areas of life using hard data.
        </p>
        <p class="about-text">
          Creator of <a href="https://frinter.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="link-teal">frinter.app</a> — 
          the <strong>WholeBeing performance system</strong> for High Performers. 
          It features the <strong>Frinter Energy Bar</strong> to help you maintain balance in the three spheres:
        </p>
        <ul class="spheres-list">
          <li><span class="sphere-dot teal"></span> <strong>Flourishing (You)</strong>: Optimizing sleep, energy, and recovery.</li>
          <li><span class="sphere-dot violet"></span> <strong>Relationships (Loved Ones)</strong>: Bringing depth and intention to social connections.</li>
          <li><span class="sphere-dot gold"></span> <strong>Deep Work (The World)</strong>: Executing high-intensity focus sprints.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="about-text">
          By extrapolating deep work principles to every sphere, I help high performers stay indexed as #1 in their field while maintaining long-term vitality.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="focus-areas">
        <div class="focus-item">
          <PixelIcon name="lightning" size={36} label="Focus Sprints" />
          <span>Focus Sprints (Frints)</span>
        </div>
        <div class="focus-item">
          <PixelIcon name="book" size={36} label="Deep Work" />
          <span>Deep Work Mastery</span>
        </div>
        <div class="focus-item">
          <PixelIcon name="tree" size={36} label="WholeBeing Optimization" />
          <span>WholeBeing Optimization</span>
        </div>
        <div class="focus-item">
          <PixelIcon name="ai" size={36} label="AI Systems" />
          <span>AI for High Performers</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    background-color: var(--bg-base);
  }
  .about-container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .about-text {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .spheres-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }
  .spheres-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
  }
  .sphere-dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }
  .sphere-dot.teal { background: var(--teal); box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--teal-glow); }
  .sphere-dot.violet { background: var(--violet); box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--violet-glow); }
  .sphere-dot.gold { background: var(--gold); box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--gold-glow); }

  .link-teal {
    color: var(--teal);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: border-color 0.15s;
  }
  .link-teal:hover { border-color: var(--teal); }
  .focus-areas {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }
  .focus-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
